Mary: The Making of a Princess





The world premiere television event Mary: The Making Of A Princess recounts the romantic story of a life-changing chance encounter in a Sydney pub that led to one of the greatest love stories the world has seen.

This made-for-TV biopic reveals the fairy tale journey of ordinary Australian Mary Donaldson (Emma Hamilton), and what she overcame for the love of Crown Prince Frederik AndrÃ© Henrik Christian of Denmark (Ryan O'Kane).
